orts fairness audits in AI deployment, ensuring explanations do not inadvertently favor certain cognitive profiles. Ultimately, PIAEE bridges the gap between objective explanation validity and subjective human comprehension, offering a scalable, data-driven path toward truly human-centered XAI evaluation.",
